cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is about training accurate Transformer machine-translation models to run inference using 8-bit integer (INT8) hardware matrix multipliers. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories related to natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
